data.value: ===================== ●功能：可对《黑神话:悟空》的游戏存档进行快速备份或还原操作，方便回档达成某些成就、重新打怪、获得错过的物品等。 ●存档还原说明：将还原【所选中的存档】【最后一次上香】或【最后一次游戏自动保存】时的进度 Function: Quickly backup or recover game save of "Black Myth Wukong". ===================== ●程序作者(Credit): ZJHCOFI ●开源地址(Open source): https://github.com/zjhcofi ●作者博客(Creditor's Blog): https://zjhcofi.com ●开源协议(License): BSD 3-Clause “New” or “Revised” License (https://choosealicense.com/licenses/bsd-3-clause) ===================== ●参考内容及素材来源(Reference content and material sources)： 1.《黑神话：悟空》官网(Black Myth Wukong): https://heishenhua.com 2. iconfont-阿里巴巴矢量图标库: https://www.iconfont.cn ===================== ●特别鸣谢(Special Thanks)： cnlnn: https://github.com/cnlnn Unica: https://github.com/unica-nya
